As an administrator, I want to be able to add and manage employee profiles within the app.
As an employee, I want to be able to easily clock in and out using the app.
As a manager, I want to have access to real-time attendance data and reports.
As an HR representative, I want the app to integrate with existing payroll systems for seamless processing.
As a business owner, I want customizable settings and permissions for different user roles.
